data.title: Where's That Vehicle Come From?
data.text:
Greece

You are here: kingkong home page > Where's That Vehicle Come From? > Greece

Greek vehicle registration plates start with a group of three letters, the first two indicating the city, prefecture or island of registration (followed here by their main towns to aid location). (Thanks to Vangelis Natsios.)

AH - Xanthi (Xanthi) AI - Aitolia-Akarnania (Agrinion) AK - Lakonia (Sparta (Sparti)) AM - Fokis (Amfissa) AN - Lasithion (Ay Nikolaus) AP - Argolis (Nafplio/Nafplion) AT - Arta (Arta) AX - Akhaia (Patras (Patrai))

BI - Boeotia (Voiotia) (Levadhia) BO - Magnisia (Volos)

EB - Evros (Alexandropoulos) EE - Pella (Edhessa) EM - Cyclades (Kikladhes) EP - Serrai (Serrai) EY - Lefkada/Lefkas (Lefkada/Lefkas)

HA - Ilia (Pirgos) HM - Imathia (Veroia) HN - Thesprotia (Igoumenitsa) HP - Heraklion (Iraklion) (Heraklion (Iraklion)) HK - Heraklion (Iraklion) (Heraklion (Iraklion))

IN - Yanina (Ioannina) (Yanina (Ioannina))

KA - Kardhitsa (Kardhitsa) KB - Kavala (Kavala) KE - Cephalonia (Kefallinia) (Kefallinia) KH - Evritania (Karpenision) KHY - Fire Brigade & other official vehicles KI - Kilkis (Kilkis) KM - Messinia (Kalamata, formerly Kalamai) KN - Pieria (Katerini) KO - Rodhope (Komotini) KP - Corinth (Korinthos) (Corinth (Korinthos)) KT - Kastoria (Kastoria) KX - Kos (Kos) KY - Corfu (Kerkira) (Kerkira) KZ - Kozani (Kozani)

ME - Aitolia-Akarnania (Mesolonghion) MH - Limnos (Myrina) MI - Fthiotis (Lamia) MO - Samos (Samos) MY - Lesbos (Lesvos) (Mitilini)

NA - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NB - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NE - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NH - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NI - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NM - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NN - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NO - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NP - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NT - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NX - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NY - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki)) NZ - Salonica (Thessaloniki) (Salonica (Thessaloniki))

XA - Euboea (Evvoia) (Khalkis) XI - Khios (Khios) XK - Khalkidhiki (Poliyiros) XN - Canea (Khania) (Canea (Khania))
